detailed or rich as the original. This doesn’t render the converted file unwatchable; many probably won’t notice the degradation in sound, but those who appreciate a robust audio experience will be sorely disappointed.","It takes about 1.5 hours to convert a feature-length movie with this program, and it yields a perfectly manageable file that won’t take up too much space on your iPad. Our test conversion yielded a 1.68GB file. Of course, the size of your file will vary from conversion to conversion, but you won’t have to worry about filling up the storage space on your iPad with bloated video files.","The major factor that keeps this application at the bottom of our review is the fact that it is missing most of the customization options we look for in this category. You can adjust technical aspects of your video, such as resolution and bit rate, but the program has no tools that allow you to trim, crop or adjust the picture values of the DVD you want to convert. The best programs come with basic video editing tools that allow you to tailor your conversion so you get exactly what you want. With 123 Copy DVD Gold, what you see on your original disc is what you get in the conversion."]},"id":"3ca77b59-a7d6-4d4e-8178-77d2d3f2d769","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"bf2377b1-46fc-4cdb-9114-ae4dc58c5831","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["123 Copy DVD Gold is a useful DVD toolbox that has a lot of great features. One of those features converts your DVD movies for playback on your iPad. It works as far as it goes, but bad sound quality and the omission of several of the key attributes we look for kept it at the rear of our lineup of the best products in this category."]},"id":"e127d999-2a4f-47d7-909f-5e299c1a707c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_66476","url":"/123-copy-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"danny-chadwick","url":"/author/danny-chadwick","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Danny Chadwick","dateModif